options compress = yes;

***********************************************************************************************
***********************************************************************************************
***********************************************************************************************

CODE NOTES:
**PONI = Previously Opioid Naive Individual. 
--no opioid script for 2 years from run out of previous script or no opioid script in 2019/2020
--cohort years -> 2021-2023
**PONI Date = Date of script meeting PONI criteria

CURES to KASPER variable relationship::
KASPER Varname						CURES Varname						    Variable Definition
CLUST_NUM						    patient_id							    Patient encrypted identifier
PATIENT_STATE					    patient_state						    State of residence listed for patient
PATIENT_ZIP						    patient_zip							    Zip code listed for patient
PATIENT_DOB						    patient_birth_year						Patient birth year
PATIENT_GENDER					    patient_gender						  	Patient sex
PRESCRIBER_ID					    prescriber_id						    Prescriber encrypted identifier
PRESCRIBER_POSTAL_CODE				prescriber_zip						  	Zip code listed for prescriber
FILLED_AT						    date_filled							    Date prescription was filled
NDC								    ndcnum								    National drug code corresponding to filled medication
DISPENSARY_ID					    pharmacy_id							    Pharmacy encrypted identifier
DISPENSARY_POSTAL_CODE				pharmacy_zip						    Zip code listed for pharmacy
DAYS_SUPPLY						    days_supply							    Days supply of medication dispensed
QUANTITY						    quantity							    Quantity of medication in prescription

***********************************************************************************************
***********************************************************************************************
***********************************************************************************************;

